race.comment: UNLEASH SHIRLEY (7) could not have been more impressive a few runs back in her powerful 29.25 win at Gosford over 515m then has finished in the placings in both runs since. Rates a leading chance if runs up to recent winning time. HER REASON (1) is better than last start when fourth (30.19) from Box 7 at this track over 520m. Comes through a solid form race last start. Shapes as one to consider. OZZIE NICK (8) is a last-start placegetter worth considering. Something for the Multiples: SMOOTH WHITE (6)
